# Project Overview

This is a Next.js project using TypeScript.

## Key Files and Directories

*   **Main Application Code**: [app](mdc:app)
*   **Public Assets**: [public](mdc:public)
*   **Components**: [components](mdc:components)
*   **Styling**: [styles](mdc:styles)
*   **Internationalization (i18n)**: [i18n](mdc:i18n)
*   **Library Code/Utilities**: [lib](mdc:lib)
*   **Type Definitions**: [types](mdc:types)
*   **Providers**: [providers](mdc:providers)

## Configuration Files

*   **Package Management**: [package.json](mdc:package.json)
*   **Next.js Configuration**: [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts)
*   **Tailwind CSS Configuration**: [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts)
*   **TypeScript Configuration**: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
*   **Biome Linter/Formatter Configuration**: [biome.json](mdc:biome.json)
